"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423225","Cabinet Office","false","2015-10-27","<p>The independent Advisory Committee on Business Appointments has confirmed that it met on 21 October, when the minutes of its previous meeting on 3 June were approved. The minutes of the June meeting have now been published on the Committee’s website in the normal way at:</p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=advisory-committee-on-business-appointments&amp;publication_type=transparency-data" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=advisory-committee-on-business-appointments&amp;publication_type=transparency-data</a></p><p>The minutes of the October meeting will be published in due course.</p>","West Suffolk","Matthew Hancock",,"2015-10-27T17:12:12.32Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423225/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423225/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423225/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2015-10-22","Business Appointments Advisory Committee","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, for what reasons the minutes of the Advisory Committee on Business Appointments have not been published since February 2015.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","13108"
