21","Double Taxation: Treaties","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what consultation they undertake prior to, or during, negotiations with a developing country on a taxation treaty.","false","Biography information for Lord McConnell of Glenscorrodale",,"Lord McConnell of Glenscorrodale","HL2843"
