n or in adulthood.</p>","Staffordshire Moorlands","Karen Bradley","12851 ; 12853","2015-10-29T17:36:48.263Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/422988/answer","Biography information for Karen Bradley","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/422988/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/422988/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2015-10-21","Offences against Children","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what training her Department provides to police officers and social workers for interviewing children and vulnerable adults who are possible victims of child abuse.","false","Biography information for Mr Barry Sheerman","Huddersfield","Mr Barry Sheerman","12852"
